### ============================================================
### Nexus BBS — 后端接口测试
### 使用方式: 按编号顺序执行，token 和 ID 会自动捕获
### ============================================================

# 基础地址
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080


### ============================================================
### 一、用户模块 (无需 token)
### ============================================================

### 1-1 注册普通用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/register
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=testuser1&password=123456

### 1-2 普通用户登录 — 自动捕获 userToken
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=testuser1&password=123456

> {% client.global.set("userToken", response.body.token); %}

### 1-3 管理员登录 — 自动捕获 adminToken (SYS_ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=YellowToTruth&password=123456

> {% client.global.set("adminToken", response.body.token); %}


### ============================================================
### 二、用户信息 (需要 token)
### ============================================================

### 2-1 查询当前用户详情 (普通用户)
GET {{baseUrl}}/user/detail?id=1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


### ============================================================
### 三、板块模块
### ============================================================

### 3-1 查询板块列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/board/list

### 3-2 创建板块
POST {{baseUrl}}/board/create
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

name=技术交流&description=编程技术讨论区&creatorId=1


### ============================================================
### 四、帖子模块 (需要 token)
### ============================================================

### 4-1 发帖 — 自动捕获 postId
POST {{baseUrl}}/post
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "title": "测试帖子标题",
  "content": "这是测试帖子的内容，用于验证发帖接口。",
  "boardId": 1,
  "type": "NORMAL"
}

> {% client.global.set("postId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 4-2 发帖 (悬赏帖子)
POST {{baseUrl}}/post
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "title": "悬赏求助帖",
  "content": "遇到一个技术问题，悬赏求解。",
  "boardId": 1,
  "type": "REWARD",
  "rewardPoints": 50
}

### 4-3 帖子列表 (全部)
GET {{baseUrl}}/post?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 4-4 帖子列表 (按板块筛选)
GET {{baseUrl}}/post?boardId=1&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 4-5 帖子列表 (关键词搜索)
GET {{baseUrl}}/post?keyword=测试&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 4-6 帖子列表 (按类型筛选)
GET {{baseUrl}}/post?type=REWARD&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 4-7 帖子详情 (使用自动捕获的 postId)
GET {{baseUrl}}/post/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 4-8 修改帖子
PUT {{baseUrl}}/post/{{postId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "title": "修改后的标题",
  "content": "修改后的内容。"
}

### 4-9 置顶帖子 (1=置顶, 0=取消) — 需要管理员
PUT {{baseUrl}}/post/{{postId}}/pin?status=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4-10 全局置顶帖子 — 需要管理员
PUT {{baseUrl}}/post/{{postId}}/global-pin?status=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 4-11 精华帖子 — 需要管理员
PUT {{baseUrl}}/post/{{postId}}/feature?status=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### ============================================================
### 五、评论模块 (需要 token，依赖 4-1 的 postId)
### ============================================================

### 5-1 发表评论 — 自动捕获 commentId
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "postId": {{postId}},
  "content": "这是一条测试评论。"
}

> {% client.global.set("commentId", response.body.data.id); %}

### 5-2 发表回复 (回复上一条评论)
POST {{baseUrl}}/comment
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "postId": {{postId}},
  "content": "这是对评论的回复。",
  "parentCommentId": {{commentId}}
}

### 5-3 查询帖子的评论列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/comment?postId={{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 5-4 采纳评论
PUT {{baseUrl}}/comment/{{commentId}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 5-5 删除评论 (软删除)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/comment/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 5-6 删除帖子 (软删除)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/post/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


### ============================================================
### 六、管理员模块 — 用户管理 (需要管理员 token)
### ============================================================

### 6-1 查询用户列表 (全部)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6-2 查询用户列表 (按关键词搜索)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?keyword=test&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6-3 查询用户列表 (按状态筛选)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?status=ACTIVE&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6-4 查询用户列表 (按角色筛选)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?role=USER&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6-5 查看用户详情 (含发帖数、评论数)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 6-6 重置用户密码
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/1/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "newPassword": "654321"
}

### 6-7 封禁用户
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "BANNED"
}

### 6-8 解封用户
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}


### ============================================================
### 七、管理员模块 — 帖子管理 (需要管理员 token)
### ============================================================

### 7-1 查询帖子列表 (全部)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/posts?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7-2 查询帖子列表 (按关键词搜索)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/posts?keyword=测试&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7-3 查询帖子列表 (按状态筛选 DELETED)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/posts?status=DELETED&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7-4 查询帖子列表 (按作者筛选)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/posts?authorId=1&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7-5 查看帖子详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/posts/{{postId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7-6 修改帖子状态为屏蔽
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/posts/{{postId}}/status?status=BLOCKED
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7-7 修改帖子状态为正常
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/posts/{{postId}}/status?status=NORMAL
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 7-8 批量屏蔽帖子
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/posts/batch-status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "ids": [1, 2],
  "status": "BLOCKED"
}


### ============================================================
### 八、管理员模块 — 评论管理 (需要管理员 token)
### ============================================================

### 8-1 查询评论列表 (全部)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/comments?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8-2 查询评论列表 (按关键词搜索)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/comments?keyword=测试&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8-3 查询评论列表 (按状态筛选)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/comments?status=DELETED&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8-4 查询评论列表 (按帖子筛选)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/comments?postId={{postId}}&page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8-5 查看评论详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/comments/{{commentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8-6 修改评论状态为屏蔽
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/comments/{{commentId}}/status?status=BLOCKED
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8-7 修改评论状态为正常
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/comments/{{commentId}}/status?status=NORMAL
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 8-8 批量屏蔽评论
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/comments/batch-status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "ids": [1, 2],
  "status": "BLOCKED"
}


### ============================================================
### 九、管理员模块 — 操作日志
### ============================================================

### 9-1 查询操作日志列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs?page=1&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 9-2 查询指定管理员的操作日志
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/logs?page=1&size=20&adminId=1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
